    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/e459320aa4c9367a6555e96274965fcd.poster.avif?t=1754190726\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/e459320aa4c9367a6555e96274965fcd.webm?t=1754190726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/e459320aa4c9367a6555e96274965fcd.mp4?t=1754190726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏简介：</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在遥远的外太空有一处实验基地，这里的外星人通过一种催化剂将人类转化为动物，以满足他们的某种需求。使用不同的催化剂，变身的动物形态也不相同。在这里，您是一位从实验室里逃脱的人类，在躲避敌人追杀的同时，利用获取的变身道具进行人与动物的形态变换，针对不同形态探索和解密游戏里的关卡。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/159bb78846ed7719812322da60080f96.poster.avif?t=1754190726\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/159bb78846ed7719812322da60080f96.webm?t=1754190726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/159bb78846ed7719812322da60080f96.mp4?t=1754190726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025220/extras/5a26f8d44a7e85c29d4257d8d98d2415.poster.avif?t=1754190726\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c